@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ykbutr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(0.43)
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v0 + 0.10 + tmp + 0.70)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.21 * v0 + 0.79)) / ((v0 + 0.99 * v1 + 0.37) - 0.09))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v0) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.30) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.03)))
    data[tid] = v0
